\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Tsay-ee-kah\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]_ and \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Bureau of Foreign Affairs\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]; \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Union\\nof Socialist Soldiers,\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Central Committee of the All-Russian Trade\\nUnions,\
