\[CloseCurlyQuote]s Commissars; he had deserted his post while the battle was\
\\nraging. As for the bourgeois press, here in Moscow there was no \
more\\nbourgeois press; even the City Duma had been dissolved. (See App. \
X,\\nSect. 4) Bukharin stood up, savage, logical, with a voice \
which\\nplunged and struck, plunged and struck.... Him they listened to \
with\\nshining eyes. Resolution, to support the action of the Council \
