a glory to die....\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nChapter XI\\n\\nThe Conquest of Power (See \
App. XI, Sect. 1)\\n\\n\\nDECLARATION OF THE RIGHTS OF THE PEOPLES OF RUSSIA \
(See App. XI,\\nSect. 2)\\n\\n... The first Congress of Soviets, in June of \
