Republic,\\n\\nPeople\[CloseCurlyQuote]s Commissar for \
Nationalities\\n\\nYUSSOV DJUGASHVILI-STALIN\\n\\nPresident of the Council of \
People\[CloseCurlyQuote]s Commissars\\n\\nV. ULIANOV (LENIN)\\n\\nThe Central \
