their\\nCommittees and established an iron discipline....\\n\\nAll these \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Governments\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] and \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]movements\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] had two \
characteristics in\\ncommon; they were controlled by the propertied classes, \
and they\\nfeared and detested Bolshevism....\\n\\nSteadily, amid the chaos \
