Creation of People\[CloseCurlyQuote]s Tribunals.... (See App. XI, \
Sect.\\n3)\\n\\nArmy after army, fleet after fleet, sent deputations, \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]joyfully to\\ngreet the new Government of the People.\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]\\n\\nIn front of Smolny, one day, I saw a ragged \
regiment just come from\\nthe trenches. The soldiers were drawn up before the \
great gates,\\nthin and grey-faced, looking up at the building as if God were \
in\\nit. Some pointed out the Imperial eagles over the door, \
