Zhizn_ characterised it as \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]a\\ncombination of \
demagoguery and impotence.\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]\\n\\nFrom day to day (it \
said) the Government of the People\[CloseCurlyQuote]s Commissars\\nsinks \
