\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]socialist\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] than the last.\\nBut \
in this exhibition of Socialism on Paper--more likely designed\\nfor the \
stupefaction of our descendants--there appears neither the\\ndesire nor the \
