\[CloseCurlyQuote]s Soviets, resolved that,\\nalthough unalterably opposed to \
the \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]criminal politics\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] of \
the\\nBolsheviki, they would, \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]in order to halt the \
