right to do so, but\\nour duty.... We have won the right to sit with the \
Bolsheviki here\\nwithin the walls of Smolny Institute, and to speak from \
this\\ntribune. After the bitter internal party struggle, we shall \
be\\nobliged, if you refuse to compromise, to pass to open \
battle\\noutside.... We must propose to the democracy terms of an \
acceptable\\ncompromise....\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]\\n\\nAfter a recess to \
consider this ultimatum, the Bolsheviki returned\\nwith a resolution, read by \
