the\\nadministration of the Municipalities and Zemstvos.\\n\\n6. All articles \
of existing laws applying to these matters are\\nherewith repealed.\\n\\n7. \
The present decree becomes effective on the day it is published\\nand applied \
by the Soviets of Workers\[CloseCurlyQuote], Soldiers\[CloseCurlyQuote] and \
Peasants\[CloseCurlyQuote]\\nDeputies.\\n\\nThe present decree has been \
confirmed by the _Tsay-ee-kah_ at the\\nmeeting of November 23d, 1917, and \
